#EXTM3U
# Hand-curated channels not available in iptv-org / Gitee / Free-TV.
# Each entry MUST include the #EXTVLCOPT lines for the host that demands them.
# Validation will pick up these headers automatically when probing.
#
# NOTE: The Samsung "M3U IPTV" free app does NOT honor #EXTVLCOPT:http-referrer.
# Channels that need a Referer header (gg.hls2.xyz / aparatchi-hosted streams)
# will fail with PLAYER_ERROR_NOT_SUPPORTED_FILE on that app.
#
# Apps that DO honor EXTVLCOPT (test on your device):
#   - OTT Navigator (free, on Samsung Tizen Store)
#   - TiviMate
#   - IPTV Smarters Pro
#   - VLC
#
# Test channel — verifies whether the user's TV app honors EXTVLCOPT.
# If this plays, the aparatchi path is unlocked; if not, remove it.
#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="persiana-sports-1" group-title="Sports",Persiana Sports 1 (TEST)
#EXTVLCOPT:http-referrer=https://www.aparatchi.com/
#EXTVLCOPT:http-user-agent=Mozilla/5.0
https://gg.hls2.xyz/live/Persiana%20Sports/playlist.m3u8
